node.text:
My simple lunch.
My anyhow throw spring onion ended up showing a smiley face 🤣🤣 Feeling lucky oredi 😅 Or am I thinking too much 🤣

The Chilean Salmon was grilled with simple salt and pepper seasoning. And brushed with a light coating of Yakiniku sauce on the grilled surface only. .

#shcgroupbuy #grilledsalmon #salmon #salmonrecipe #salmondinner #salmonlunch #sghomecooks #cookingathome #sgcooking #sghomecooking #circuitbreakersg #circuitbreakercookingchallenge #stayhome #stayhomecooking #sghomecookedfood #igeats #instafood #instacook #instacooking #igcooking #sgfoodtrend #stayhomewithascott #iluvcooking #howtocook #howtocooksalmon
@dressacake no meh 😕, ok imagine the smiley face slap his neighbour 🤣🤣
@rontreechan You hide too long in the house liao lah! 🤣
I spotted a smiley face too!
That grill marks are so legit 🔥, no simple at all! And we love that smiley face too! Truly made our day looking at happy home cooked meals. Yums!

Thank you for pledging to #StayHomeWithAscott. #CapitaLandHopeFoundation will be making a donation of US$10 to Save The Children and we look forward to more of your #StayHomeWithAscott posts. Stay home, stay safe and cook away!
